#Helen Oliveira
## Verbo GET – listar todos
GET http://localhost:8000/cliente/
HTTP/1.1
### Verbo GET – listar um
GET http://localhost:8000/cliente/1
HTTP/1.1
### Verbo POST – adicionar
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/cliente/
content-type: application/json

{
 "nome": "Helen Oliveira",
 "cpf": "12345678900",
 "telefone": "49999999999"
}
### Verbo PUT – atualizar
PUT http://127.0.0.1:8000/cliente/1
content-type: application/json

{
 "nome": "Helen Oliveira Atualizado",
 "cpf": "12345678900",
 "telefone": "49988888888"
}
### Verbo DELETE – excluir
DELETE http://127.0.0.1:8000/cliente/1
HTTP/1.1